Get USPORTS volleyball schedule

Source: R/volleyball_schedule.R
volleyball_schedule.Rd

Get USPORTS volleyball schedule

Usage

volleyball_schedule(gender)

Arguments

gender

Gender of athletes "m" or "w"

Value

A data frame.

Examples

volleyball_schedule("m")
